      • setPaymentMethodTypes

        @NotNull
public com.stripe.android.PaymentSessionConfig.Builder setPaymentMethodTypes(@NotNull
                                                                                      java.util.List<? extends com.stripe.android.model.PaymentMethod.Type> paymentMethodTypes)
        Parameters:
        paymentMethodTypes -

        a list of enum PaymentMethod.Type that indicates the types of Payment Methods that the customer can select or add via Stripe UI components.

        The order of the enum PaymentMethod.Type values in the list will be used to arrange the add buttons in the Stripe UI components. They will be arranged vertically from first to last.

        Currently only PaymentMethod.Type.Card and PaymentMethod.Type.Fpx are supported. If not specified or empty, PaymentMethod.Type.Card will be used.
